Enum Class ProductCategory

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ProductCategory>
com.etiennecollin.ift2255.clientCLI.models.data.products.ProductCategory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ProductCategory>, Constable
public enum ProductCategory extends Enum<ProductCategory> implements Serializable
Represents the category of a product. Each category may have sub-categories represented by different enums.
